## First-time setup

If you've landed in this repo without the Memnyx workspace set up,
several skills (cross-repo memory, identity-aware reports, brag log
accumulation) won't be available. The repo works standalone, but the full
experience requires Memnyx.

To set up: clone the boilerplate source as a sibling of your workspace — for example, into
`~/src/memnyx/` — and run `/setup-workspace init`
from your chosen workspace folder. Register this project via `/hello` once
the workspace is ready.

