### Artifacts naming

Any output produced by a skill or session — feedback files, generated documents, collected data, derived artefacts — lands under this project's `artifacts/` directory, never co-located with `workstreams/` or `sessions/`.

| Output type | Path pattern |
|-------------|--------------|
| Skill output | `artifacts/<skill-slug>/<filename>` |
| Workstream artefact | `artifacts/<workstream-slug>/<filename>` |

Resolve scope from the session marker, never from cwd. Workspace-scoped artefacts live at the workspace root's `artifacts/`, not here.

